plugin_name: AI Smart Programming Assistant
plugin_description: An AI-powered smart programming assistant plugin for MT Manager, providing intelligent code analysis, optimization suggestions, and issue diagnosis services. Deeply integrated with AI model, supporting full-text analysis and quick code snippet diagnosis. Also includes practical development tools such as encoding/decoding, hash calculation, and timestamp conversion to comprehensively improve mobile programming efficiency.
plugin_author: Kang Ge
plugin_website: Official Website
about: About
features_title: Core Features
features_summary: This plugin features AI code analysis as the core function, along with various practical development tools. All functions can be used directly in the text editor to comprehensively improve programming efficiency
encode_decode_function: Encode/Decode
encode_decode_usage: Provides multiple encoding/decoding formats. Select text and click the corresponding function to use it.
base64_encode: Base64 Encode
base64_encode_usage: Encodes selected text in Base64 format.
base64_decode: Base64 Decode
hex_encode: Hex Encode
hex_encode_usage: Encodes selected text in hexadecimal format.
hex_decode: Hex Decode
unicode_encode: Unicode Encode
unicode_encode_usage: Encodes selected text as Unicode escape sequences.
unicode_decode: Unicode Decode
url_encode: URL Encode
url_decode: URL Decode
rot13_encode: ROT13 Encode
rot13_encode_usage: Encrypts selected text using ROT13 algorithm.
rot13_decode: ROT13 Decode
rot13_decode_usage: Decrypts selected text using ROT13 algorithm.
binary_encode: Binary Encode
binary_encode_usage: Encodes selected text in binary format.
binary_decode: Binary Decode
encode_decode_error: Encoding/Decoding failed
hash_function: Hash Calculation
hash_usage: Select any text to calculate the hash value (MD5/SHA-256/SHA-512) and copy to clipboard. Quickly generate text fingerprints for file integrity verification.
timestamp_function: Timestamp Conversion
timestamp_usage: Supports bidirectional conversion: Select a numeric timestamp to automatically convert to date/time format, or select a date/time string to convert to timestamp. Supports multiple date formats (yyyy-MM-dd, yyyy/MM/dd, etc.).
quick_insert_function: Insert Time
quick_insert_usage: Quickly insert the current date and time at the cursor position in yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss format. No need to select text, available anytime.
ai_code_analysis: AI Code Analysis
ai_code_analysis_usage: [Core Feature] Perform AI intelligent analysis on all code in the current editor, providing code overview, quality assessment, potential issue identification, optimization suggestions, and code standard checks. Supports real-time display of the analysis process.
ai_quick_analysis: AI Quick Analysis
ai_quick_analysis_usage: [Core Feature] Perform AI quick analysis on selected code snippets, providing targeted optimization suggestions and issue diagnosis. Select text and click to use.
